because that street
runs all over the world.

244
00:21:30,005 --> 00:21:33,065
I know because
that's the street I came from,

245
00:21:33,742 --> 00:21:37,542
6,000 miles from here
in a little English mill town.

246
00:21:38,513 --> 00:21:42,279
But it's the same rotten street,
the same factories, the same people,

247
00:21:42,351 --> 00:21:45,980
and the same
dirty little gray-faced children.

248
00:21:46,054 --> 00:21:47,385
I need you.

249
00:21:47,456 --> 00:21:48,855
Oh, it's no use, Lloyd.

250
00:21:48,924 --> 00:21:51,552
I can't go back to that
sick, unhealthy street,

251
00:21:51,626 --> 00:21:53,059
the street I came from.

252
00:21:53,128 --> 00:21:55,562
I can't go back to it. I can't, Lloyd, I won't.

253
00:21:55,630 --> 00:21:58,463
And I can't leave it. I'm a doctor.

254
00:21:58,533 --> 00:22:01,229
