261
00:22:17,986 --> 00:22:19,749
Seventy-five dollars.

262
00:22:19,821 --> 00:22:23,086
That's as much as you earn in a week
of sopping up running noses.

263
00:22:23,158 --> 00:22:25,854
A bottle of perfume, that's our reality.

264
00:22:27,596 --> 00:22:29,621
I can't do it your way.

265
00:22:30,699 --> 00:22:32,166
That's what I said.

266
00:22:53,221 --> 00:22:55,280
Doctor Craig's office.

267
00:22:55,357 --> 00:22:57,825
No, he hasn't come in yet.

268
00:22:57,893 --> 00:23:00,919
I couldn't say, he's usually in before this.

269
00:23:00,996 --> 00:23:04,329
Yes, I'll have him call you. Yes. Goodbye.

270
00:23:06,234 --> 00:23:08,225
Here, blow. Blow hard.

