292
00:24:37,325 --> 00:24:38,917
Let someone else deliver his papers.

293
00:24:38,994 --> 00:24:41,360
He's got to stay in bed at least a week.

294
00:24:41,429 --> 00:24:43,795
All right, Doctor. Thank you very much.

295
00:24:43,865 --> 00:24:45,196
Thank you.

296
00:24:58,480 --> 00:25:00,471
Do you want your call list now?

297
00:25:00,549 --> 00:25:02,244
- Tear it up.
- What?

298
