302
00:25:12,994 --> 00:25:14,188
What do you mean,
what's happened to me?

303
00:25:14,262 --> 00:25:17,129
Nothing's happened to me.
I'm tired, that's all.

304
00:25:17,199 --> 00:25:20,600
Tired of patients, tired of my work,
tired of this shabby neighborhood.

305
00:25:20,669 --> 00:25:22,296
And are you tired of...

306
00:25:22,771 --> 00:25:25,865
No, I won't give you a chance to say it.

307
00:25:32,547 --> 00:25:34,310
Good night, Lloyd.

308
00:26:46,021 --> 00:26:47,010
Darling?

309
00:26:50,091 --> 00:26:53,288
That's why I asked to have
you brought here first, Miss Shelby.

310
00:26:53,361 --> 00:26:54,350
Guard.

311
00:26:54,429 --> 00:26:57,227
He won't speak to me,
refuses even to see me,

312
00:26:57,299 --> 00:26:59,995
and there are so few precious hours left.

313
00:27:00,068 --> 00:27:03,231
If you could only make him realize...

314
00:27:13,548 --> 00:27:14,776
Here we are.

315
00:27:16,885 --> 00:27:18,512
Hello, Frankie.

316
00:27:27,696 --> 00:27:28,685
Margot.

317
00:27:29,798 --> 00:27:32,130
- What time is it?
- 5:00.

318
00:27:32,634 --> 00:27:34,261
Three more hours.

319
00:27:35,603 --> 00:27:38,037
Come here, baby. I want to look at you.

320
00:27:40,809 --> 00:27:43,004
New dress you got, isn't it?

321
00:27:43,078 --> 00:27:45,569
And the gloves and the shoes.

322
00:27:45,647 --> 00:27:47,444
And that silly little hat.

323
00:27:48,516 --> 00:27:52,384
Oh, you're beautiful, Margot. So beautiful.

324
00:27:53,188 --> 00:27:55,588
You're the only thing I hate to leave.

325
00:27:56,391 --> 00:27:58,655
Maybe you won't have to, Frankie.

326
00:27:59,094 --> 00:28:00,425
What do you mean?

327
00:28:00,862 --> 00:28:02,352
Listen, and don't interrupt.

328
00:28:02,430 --> 00:28:04,261
And I don't understand.

329
00:28:04,332 --> 00:28:06,391
What is it that makes them
willing to die without...

330
00:28:06,468 --> 00:28:07,992
Yes, sir.

331
00:28:08,069 --> 00:28:09,764
Yes? Yes, what?

332
00:28:09,838 --> 00:28:11,430
Oh, well... That is...

333
00:28:11,506 --> 00:28:13,906
So, see the Chaplain, Frankie.

