00:29:45,567 --> 00:29:47,762
C- H-O-T, shot.

337
00:29:47,836 --> 00:29:50,100
O- M-Y. Dishotomy.

338
00:29:52,841 --> 00:29:54,468
Ain't that a lulu?

339
00:29:54,542 --> 00:29:57,636
And get this one, didactic.

340
00:29:59,314 --> 00:30:02,181
Hey, why don't you stop reading that junk?

341
00:30:02,250 --> 00:30:04,047
What's the matter with the dictionary?

342
00:30:04,118 --> 00:30:06,177
There ain't enough story to it.

343
00:30:09,891 --> 00:30:11,825
All right, boys, bring him in.

344
00:30:18,766 --> 00:30:21,462
- Anything else, Doc?
- That's all, thanks.

345
00:30:30,979 --> 00:30:34,938
- Okay, wrap him up.
- Hey, Doc, what about the autopsy?

346
00:30:36,117 --> 00:30:39,553
- What have I done now?
- You would have to bring that up.

347
00:30:39,621 --> 00:30:41,282
We can skip it tonight, boys.

348
00:30:41,356 --> 00:30:45,019
There's somebody waiting for me
and it's kind of late.

349
00:30:45,093 --> 00:30:46,492
Okay, Doc.

350
00:30:46,561 --> 00:30:48,153
Come on and help me with the box, Benny.

351
00:30:48,229 --> 00:30:49,753
- Who, me?
- Yeah, you.

352
00:30:49,831 --> 00:30:50,889
Oh.

353
00:31:33,541 --> 00:31:35,839
No, not like that.

354
00:31:35,910 --> 00:31:40,313
How many times do I have to tell you?
Fold it like this.

355
00:31:41,215 --> 00:31:43,342
Now, what's wrong
with the way I'm doing it?

356
00:31:43,418 --> 00:31:46,649
Benny, don't be obfuscatory.

357
00:31:52,860 --> 00:31:54,691
- Call Pete.
- Who, me?

358
00:31:54,762 --> 00:31:56,753
- Yeah, you.
- Oh.

359
00:31:57,432 --> 00:32:00,060
- Nice and tidy, Doc.
- Hey, Pete!

360
00:32:00,134 --> 00:32:01,726
Okay for the pick up.

361
00:32:24,626 --> 00:32:26,617
Here's the order for cremation.

362
00:32:29,497 --> 00:32:31,795
- All right, Pete.
- That'll be all for tonight, Doc?

363
00:32:31,866 --> 00:32:34,334
That's all, boys, thank you. Good night.

364
00:32:34,402 --> 00:32:36,302
- Good night.
- Good night, Doc.

365
00:32:37,805 --> 00:32:41,798
Dishotomy, what a beautiful word.

366
00:32:42,210 --> 00:32:43,734
Dishotomy.

367
00:32:44,345 --> 00:32:45,607
Chotomy.

368
00:32:52,320 --> 00:32:54,880
