showing the place where I hid the dough.

464
00:47:32,566 --> 00:47:35,899
Now, in case I don't pull through
the operation okay, Margot pays off.

465
00:47:35,969 --> 00:47:37,527
Is that okay, Jim?

466
00:47:37,604 --> 00:47:39,595
It's okay by me, Frankie.

467
00:48:16,743 --> 00:48:19,439
Here you are, baby. Here's your protection.

468
00:48:19,513 --> 00:48:23,506
You don't have to be afraid any longer.
You see, I do think about you.

469
00:48:25,152 --> 00:48:28,610
- What have you done?
- I also think about myself.

470
00:48:30,357 --> 00:48:32,917
Don't be so disappointed, beautiful.

471
00:48:33,327 --> 00:48:36,524
In case anything happens to me,
I'll still be wearing these clothes.

472
00:48:36,597 --> 00:48:39,896
Your protection
will be waiting for you right here.

473
00:48:39,967 --> 00:48:42,265
- I'll go for the doctor now.
- Wait.

474
00:48:43,136 --> 00:48:45,798
You haven't kissed me yet, Margot.

475
00:48:45,872 --> 00:48:49,330
No, Frankie. Not now, there isn't time.

476
00:48:49,409 --> 00:48:51,969
You're wrong, baby.
There's time, plenty of time.

477
00:48:52,045 --> 00:48:55,173
Just a little kiss,
a little welcome back kiss.

478
00:48:55,248 --> 00:48:57,978
- There isn't time, Frankie.
- Why not?

479
00:48:58,051 --> 00:48:59,678
Why not, Jimmy boy?

480
00:48:59,753 --> 00:49:01,653
Why shouldn't I kiss my girl?

481
00:49:01,722 --> 00:49:03,849
My little Margot,
who doesn't have to worry anymore

482
00:49:03,924 --> 00:49:06,415
about what's going to happen to her
after I die.

483
00:49:27,547 --> 00:49:28,809
Margot!

484
00:50:18,632 --> 00:50:20,156
Dr. Craig?

485
00:50:22,669 --> 00:50:25,365
Just dropped around for a visit

486
00:50:27,808 --> 00:50:29,070
inside.

487
00:51:31,404 --> 00:51:33,838
Gotta be an engineer too, eh, Doc?

488
00:51:38,311 --> 00:51:39,539
Doc,

489
00:51:41,548 --> 00:51:44,346
I came over to find out
about Frankie Olins.

490
00:51:47,621 --> 00:51:49,555
What about Frankie Olins?

491
00:51:51,224 --> 00:51:52,885
You sign that?

